The goal is to show `IsBinomialRandom (fun ω => (G ω)ᶜ) (σ p) P`.
This means we need to show that `fun ω => (G ω)ᶜ` has the law `binomialRandom V (σ p)`.

We have `hG : IsBinomialRandom G p P`, which means `G` has the law `binomialRandom V p`.
