`⊢ Measure.map (fun ω => (G ω)ᶜ) P = @SimpleGraph.binomialRandom V (unitInterval.symm p)`

This means we need to show that the measure obtained by mapping the complement operation over the graphs (i.e., `G ω ↦ (G ω)ᶜ`) applied to `P` is equal to the binomial random graph measure with parameter `1-p` (which is `unitInterval.symm p`).

